snippet.title: 3D Pocket Pool - Game Boy Color
snippet.description:
This is a complete playthrough of 3D Pocket Pool for the Gameboy Color.
Review and scores in description.

Pros 
 +  Characters play a good role during play
 +  Lots of different modes
 +  Different style of play to most pool games

Cons
 -  Sound isn't nice after a while


Score (out of 100)

 Graphics   :=  88
 Sound   :=  60
 Controls   :=  87
 Gameplay  :=  72
 Replayability  :=  82
 Enjoyment  :=  74
 Technical  :=  75

 Overall   :=  83

Gaming Exhibit Score  :=  77.6%

Synopsis
A great version of a pool game with lots of character and a playstyle that lets you 'snooker' your opponent easier.
